Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.13,0:01:34.51,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Moonlight
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.18,0:02:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.14,0:02:29.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But don't move away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.53,0:02:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kyouko was like a glass that had cracks in it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.57,0:02:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No matter how much water you poured into it,\Nit would never be filled.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.50,0:02:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She has a family, is blessed with good looks,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.42,0:02:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and possesses the power\Nto control the people around her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.71,0:02:57.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And yet, like an animal that is always starving,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.34,0:03:00.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}loneliness ate into her heart.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.35,0:03:07.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And the ones who put those cracks\Ninto her glass were none other than...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.69,0:03:13.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}my adoptive father...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.27,0:03:15.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.70,0:03:22.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.95,0:03:25.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in love with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.00,0:03:28.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That guy is no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.83,0:03:30.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He has a wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.50,0:03:32.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's been in the hospital forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.88,0:03:35.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's been alone all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.21,0:03:37.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dad won't forgive you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.26,0:03:39.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.18,0:03:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't forgive him either.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.10,0:03:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.85,0:03:52.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He branded his own daughter a failure when\Nshe was just a 2nd-year middle school student.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.23,0:04:01.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He said, "There are other things in life\Nthan shogi," when he didn't even mean it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.66,0:04:04.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.24,0:04:05.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shogi isn't everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.79,0:04:08.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lie to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.37,0:04:13.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When shogi is the only thing\Nyou and Dad think about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.92,0:04:15.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've had enough already.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.54,0:04:20.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Both of you look at me like I'm a loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.05,0:04:24.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You tiptoe around me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.56,0:04:28.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's infuriating.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.97,0:04:32.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How long do I have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.98,0:04:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,feel this pathetic?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.69,0:04:41.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.74,0:04:47.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No matter where I go,\Nno one will worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.70,0:04:50.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But it's different with you, Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.25,0:04:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're important to Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.13,0:04:58.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,even if you think otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.89,0:05:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}In all things, the path\Nshould have a teacher or a guide.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.30,0:05:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}10:00 am.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.27,0:05:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The match is starting.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.39,0:05:16.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The finals of the tournament to determine\Nthe challenger for the Lion King title.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.65,0:05:18.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The first game of three.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.32,0:05:21.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right now, in a special match room,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.24,0:05:26.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}those two are quietly facing each other.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.83,0:05:35.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder what kind of fight it'll be.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.58,0:05:40.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When I was playing against Mr. Shimada,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.46,0:05:42.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was seized by a strange sensation.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.80,0:05:46.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I felt like I stepped into a sea of trees.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.59,0:05:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Like I became enmeshed\Nin something overpowering...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.39,0:05:55.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Like something was silently\Ntightening around me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.19,0:06:00.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What kind of game will he play against Gotou?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.86,0:06:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Faculty Room
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.65,0:06:06.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Hayashida, I have\Nmy absence notices for March.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.28,0:06:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kiriyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.41,0:06:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this. It's incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.70,0:06:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Two hours in and this is where they're at.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.75,0:06:16.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.79,0:06:20.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just by looking at the moves played so far,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.34,0:06:26.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}it felt like I could hear the dull sound\Nof heavy bones colliding with each other.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.18,0:06:30.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wondered how those two\N"solemn" guys would play against each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.51,0:06:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But it looks like a slugfest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.01,0:06:34.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Man, that's crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.15,0:06:43.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.57,0:06:46.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.53,0:06:47.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Shogi Hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.15,0:06:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.16,0:06:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't a Title Match,\Nso this blog updates irregularly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.24,0:06:56.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't it be a better learning experience\Nif you watched it directly?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.16,0:06:59.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I've got so many absences...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.13,0:07:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.34,0:07:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine, just go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.09,0:07:11.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Attendance Records
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.63,0:07:11.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,H-He has enough, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.34,0:07:15.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Thump-Thump-Thump
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.59,0:07:14.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1-2-3... Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.39,0:07:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just barely, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.35,0:07:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'm not qualified to be a teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.48,0:07:21.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Shogi Hall
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.65,0:07:31.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}- Hey, Kiriyama.\N- Kiriyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.16,0:07:38.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- He made a move.\N- The left 4-c-Gold?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.83,0:07:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No way. I've never seen\NMr. Shimada like this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.75,0:07:44.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is he throwing away his Bishop here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.30,0:07:48.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen Brother\Nplay like this before either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.68,0:07:54.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It felt like their presence\Nhad passed from the special match room,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.51,0:07:59.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}through the dark hallway,\Nand seeped into this room.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.42,0:08:23.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.13,0:08:26.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How? What's different?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.55,0:08:30.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why does each move pull me in?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.60,0:08:39.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is it the amount of time they've spent?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.81,0:08:45.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The depth of their accumulated experience?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.23,0:08:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The weight of their sacrifices?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.90,0:08:53.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Or is it all of that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.62,0:09:00.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right. This is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.04,0:09:06.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}a battle between two people...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.63,0:09:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}who have faith in themselves.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.22,0:09:16.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The match ended at 9 pm.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.22,0:09:20.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After 153 moves,\NShimada 8th-Dan conceded defeat.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.77,0:09:25.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The first of three games\Nfor the Lion King Finals Tournament{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.10,0:09:28.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}ended with victory for Gotou 9th-Dan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.40,0:09:33.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.83,0:09:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This place hasn't changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.95,0:09:43.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Such a dreary building.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.16,0:09:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I used to hate it.\NThis dark street, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.63,0:09:49.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And the gloomy shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.63,0:09:51.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.80,0:09:56.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.89,0:10:00.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well. My two stalkers together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.51,0:10:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kyouko, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.72,0:10:03.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.40,0:10:11.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And you were so excited\Nto play a match with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.40,0:10:15.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?\NShimada was really strong, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.70,0:10:18.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate a Rank A.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.79,0:10:30.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey. Are you really leaving?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.21,0:10:33.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I didn't want to move away.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.38,0:10:34.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.93,0:10:42.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are you running away... from me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.85,0:10:46.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I couldn't be with her anymore.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.15,0:10:52.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was in a hurry to become an adult.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.98,0:10:57.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I thought if I couldn't stand\Non my own two feet,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.83,0:11:04.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}there was no way I could protect...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.79,0:11:09.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}those who were dear to me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.38,0:11:16.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.09,0:11:19.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When I tried to take the initiative\Nwith the one-turn loss bishop exchange,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.30,0:11:24.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that bastard fought back right away.\NAnd he was cheerful about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.81,0:11:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That old man really is tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.23,0:11:28.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And he's scary! That face...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.15,0:11:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But on top of being strong,\Nhe's not very mature.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.82,0:11:35.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.86,0:11:38.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I swear I won't lose next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.78,0:11:41.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.07,0:11:43.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.04,0:11:48.04,Next Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Moonlight
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.04,0:11:51.04,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lump of Ego
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.55,0:11:57.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Mikazuki-Dou
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.71,0:11:57.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.80,0:11:58.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Blush!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.17,0:12:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't have been able to visit either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.89,0:12:07.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Full of vigor in front of you girls,\Nbut he sunk before getting to the main event?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.81,0:12:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.52,0:12:12.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For a boy, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.52,0:12:15.15,DefaultLeftH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seems to be recalling\Ndifferent happenings\Nfrom his youth
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.15,0:12:20.65,CenterSignM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Twitch\NTwitch
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.15,0:12:20.65,DefaultLeftH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fidget\NFidget
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.44,0:12:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If it were me, I'd slit my belly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.40,0:12:20.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'd shave off one eyebrow\Nand seclude myself in the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.20,0:12:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really something that shameful?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.62,0:12:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't have to worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.37,0:12:35.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He said he would do his best\Nand I'm sure he did, knowing Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.38,0:12:40.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it didn't work out,\Nno one would laugh at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.05,0:12:41.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.38,0:12:43.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shame has value, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.84,0:12:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because "failing" means\Nhe "challenged" something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.06,0:12:53.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's hell of a lot better than a life\Nof doing nothing, and laughing at other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.56,0:12:58.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The thing is, the kid's still young\Nand too damn serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.40,0:13:01.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He must really have wanted\Nto beat that player.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.90,0:13:06.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That was the first time I ever saw Rei\Nshow such fighting spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.99,0:13:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I suppose he bit off\Nmore than he could chew.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.42,0:13:19.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I bet he's eating just sweet bread and ramen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.09,0:13:23.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do at a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.76,0:13:25.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You just gotta leave him be.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.55,0:13:30.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The only way to make up\Nfor a blunder at work is at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.64,0:13:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Until the kid can think,\N"I made good," all he can do is his best.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.94,0:13:42.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, eventually, when he becomes an adult,\Nhe'll realize it, like it or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.49,0:13:45.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That out of all the people\Nwho've put themselves out there,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.99,0:13:50.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,every single one has been\Nhumiliated at some point.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.95,0:13:53.00,EpNum,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shogi Hall
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.34,0:14:05.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You know, Shimada, recently,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.09,0:14:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you look older than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.64,0:14:11.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you looking?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.06,0:14:16.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It must be tough\Nmaintaining that muscular chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.19,0:14:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Have you secretly been hitting the gym?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.94,0:14:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Narcissists have it rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.91,0:14:29.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.24,0:14:32.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.68,0:14:48.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That was cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.05,0:14:50.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What was that mature presence?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.35,0:14:51.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what they were talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.93,0:14:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Brother is so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.64,0:14:57.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rank A, huh? If you become Rank A,\Ndo you naturally exude that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.56,0:15:02.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Strange. I can't smell the slightest bit of it\Nfrom myself. That presence...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.40,0:15:06.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right now I'm B-1, but if I move up to Rank A,\Nwill I suddenly smell like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.86,0:15:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you will! I bet it'll be like an aura!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.57,0:15:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.20,0:15:13.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Their match is going to start!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.41,0:15:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you guys ever will have "it."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.37,0:15:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not as long as you spy on people\Nfrom behind bushes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.04,0:15:26.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}At the end of World War I, as you can see,\Nthe strong recovery of productivity...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.51,0:15:29.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}10:00... The match is starting.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.34,0:15:33.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Three matches to determine\Nthe challenger for the Lion King.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.06,0:15:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gotou 9th-Dan won the first match.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.52,0:15:39.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is Mr. Shimada's last chance.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.48,0:15:44.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In the previous match, they did the unexpected\Nand engaged in a slugfest,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.40,0:15:47.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but what kind of battle will it be this time?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.28,0:15:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to watch it. I want to watch it so badly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.87,0:15:52.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.95,0:15:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! I finished calculating\Nyour days of attendance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.32,0:15:53.83,LeftSignM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Bam{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.32,0:15:56.70,OnTop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Attendance Records
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.95,0:16:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And I've come to the conclusion that you can't\Ncatch a cold or even get appendicitis.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.04,0:16:05.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You've got two scheduled days off\Nfor rank-deciding matches,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.13,0:16:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so we can't do anything about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.51,0:16:11.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But if you happen to advance in any\Nof the tournaments, you'll be in real danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.64,0:16:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Also, in case something happens, aim to get\Nabove average scores on the year-end tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.77,0:16:21.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As for which parts to study for the test...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.39,0:16:26.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,if I said, "Ask a friend!" the exams would be\Nover and you'd still be looking for a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.02,0:16:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So instead, I asked\Nall of the teachers on your behalf.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.69,0:16:31.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here. Don't lose it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.16,0:16:34.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be tough if you have to repeat a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.57,0:16:37.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your classmates might call you "old man"!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.66,0:16:39.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.62,0:16:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is a big help.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.46,0:16:49.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But... what is this feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.43,0:16:56.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Shogi Hall
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.01,0:16:56.93,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.43,0:16:58.93,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,in the special match room...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.43,0:17:01.43,LeftSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Boom
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.64,0:17:39.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A slugfest. Another one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.18,0:17:42.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're locked together even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.56,0:17:45.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, they're using even more\Nbrute force than last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.73,0:17:46.48,RightSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bam!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.23,0:17:49.48,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For some reason,\Neveryone is sitting straight...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.48,0:17:47.48,RightSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bang!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.48,0:17:48.48,RightSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Slap!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.48,0:17:49.48,RightSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bam!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.69,0:17:51.86,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so, eight hours later...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.86,0:17:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.61,0:17:55.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,both of them are entering\Ntheir kings into the fray!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.99,0:17:59.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop! That's immature!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.08,0:18:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who thinks, "Since it's come to this,\NI'll win if I play the king?"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.90,0:18:34.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That was thunder!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.53,0:18:37.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's no time to be laughing at glowing pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.70,0:18:40.20,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And three more hours later...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.34,0:18:56.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Stagger Stagger
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.30,0:19:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I won, kiddo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.43,0:19:05.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Brother, that was awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.73,0:19:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,W-With just one game?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.98,0:19:13.11,SMR,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Youngsters afraid\Nof the magnitude\Nof what's been lost
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.36,0:19:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, kiddo?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.24,0:19:22.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, nothing. Just that Kiriyama\Nhasn't replied to my text.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.28,0:19:28.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Maybe I went a little too far\Nknocking his lights out that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.26,0:19:46.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Shogi Hall
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.51,0:19:46.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me, kiddo. Why are you so interested\Nin having Kiriyama get better?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.06,0:19:49.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kiriyama...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.60,0:19:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kiriyama is the one...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.65,0:19:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,who broke my head in half,\Nthen pulled me from the mud.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.95,0:20:04.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I spent a lot of time in the hospital\Never since I was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.29,0:20:09.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Getting better at the board\Nwas my sole emotional support.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.17,0:20:17.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,While watching my peers\Nhaving fun and playing outside
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.67,0:20:19.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,from the corner of my eye,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.59,0:20:22.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I would keep myself immersed in shogi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.30,0:20:26.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}46th Children's Shogi Tournament
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.01,0:20:29.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And yet, the stronger I got,\Nthe more I wrote off my weaker opponents
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.68,0:20:32.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,as cowards who didn't even bother\Nmaking an effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.61,0:20:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was so frustrating\Nand annoying and irritating.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.65,0:20:41.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, after being reduced to a lump of ego...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.29,0:20:53.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.50,0:20:57.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Water.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.59,0:21:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I met Kiriyama...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.18,0:21:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,he split my head in half...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.72,0:21:11.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.90,0:21:15.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There is someone stronger than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.19,0:21:18.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There is someone\Nwho worked harder than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.19,0:21:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not alone... is what I realized.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.74,0:21:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.87,0:21:34.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I understand that. Kind of.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.13,0:21:36.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.42,0:21:41.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.26,0:21:48.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! I said, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.23,0:21:59.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell? Gotou, you moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.32,0:22:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.94,0:22:05.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... Gotou, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.11,0:22:06.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, he's married...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.61,0:22:10.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that beautiful... and... young...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.04,0:22:12.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What was that? An argument?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.92,0:22:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}What is this sense of defeat?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.13,0:22:26.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, that was nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.26,0:22:25.13,LeftSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Swing
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.01,0:22:29.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! I swear I'll win the next one, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.80,0:22:33.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, kiddo. Let's get back\Nand plan a strategy for the final match.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.98,0:22:37.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! There it is! That's the Brother I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.81,0:22:40.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, over to Kiriyama...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.52,0:22:44.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Hayashida found a grave miscalculation.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.19,0:22:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Filling in the gaps with many reports.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.70,0:22:51.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...\NYou were actually already two days short.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.28,0:22:53.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay, Mr. Hayashida.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.41,0:22:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Really, it's like...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.50,0:23:00.04,Next Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lump of Ego
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.92,0:22:58.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I'm the one who's sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.01,0:24:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.01,0:24:37.22,EpNum,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 16
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.47,0:24:37.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, what shall we do for this year's\NGirls' Festival at our house?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.43,0:24:39.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, should we start?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.64,0:24:42.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! I forgot the main reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.31,0:24:45.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If he never comes to visit,\NI'll stop caring about him!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.57,0:24:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Inari-san, let's hurry and eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.86,0:24:54.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"March Comes in Like a Lion".\NHey, Gotou, you better watch it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.82,0:24:58.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know, already!\NYou better not miss it either.
